opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 26th day of September, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and the Application for an Immediate Hearing are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
